OpenAI Chat API Reference
OpenAI Vision Guide
Sample images used
Here is an example of how to analyze an image using the OpenAI API.
curlhttps://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions\-H"Content-Type: application/json"\-H"Authorization: Bearer$OPENAI_API_KEY"\-d'{
    "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
    "messages": [
      {
        "role": "user",
        "content": [
          {"type": "text", "text": "What is in this image?"},
          {
            "type": "image_url",
            "detail": "low",
            "image_url": {"url": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/34/Correlation_coefficient.png"}
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
